Angular JS - GDI SF 2015

DOM -
-how you interact with your html & javascript to manipulate the browser
-code behind what appears on the page

NG-directives
-wrap expressions in click event functions rather than including it in your html
-use directives for reusable components -

CUSTOM DIRECTIVES
-scope without the dollar sign is connected to the controller that is connected to your view
-a way for the directive to communicate with your controller 

SERVICE
-a way of getting data for your application
Custom Services
-called FACTORIES
-don't do HTTP REQUESTS in the controller - NOT BEST PRACTICE!!